{
  "stem": "11472.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know, the people shared homes.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Well, going back to the-- to the trap that they made for our men.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "All the men started to go.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "My grandmother said to her sons, wait.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My father got dressed, he was going.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My grandma says, where are you going?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Just take it easy.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Don't run.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He said, I'm to Borschtov.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because he had an uncle.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He says, I'll go and I'll see my aunt and uncle.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She says, just a minute.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You wait.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And she took off her Jewish star, she put on a shawl, and she started to walk up the road.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "She said she was going to go-- it was a market day that day.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And she was going to go and try to see.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Make believe she's a peasant and see what was going on.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And she didn't have to leave our town.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Because another girl did the same thing, because she came running.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "She said, the people are being let in, and nobody's-- they don't let nobody out.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "That trap was made for five towns-- Borschtov, Korolowka, Mielec, Szcala, and I think Clustov.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Anyway, all these men were trapped and they were never heard of.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And we started to see that we can't trust the Germans, because what they tell us is never true.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And they're just trapping us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "They're just tricking us.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Because we're Jews, we were hoping-- we were trying to believe them.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "We were hoping maybe, maybe they'll take some boys, and they'll leave the population alone.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "But then, all of a sudden, we started to hear that there's such a thing as-- before I go to the aktias, I'd like to tell you.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "A man from Borschtov, from the Judenrat, came to our town.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
